{"tid":303111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"駐香港解放軍實比人調教，派日本三菱原子筆比記者","createTime":"2017-06-30T02:10:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T13:34:50.000Z","uid":51271,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0fe39e3deb561612ce38c421d7cc81d130404432","tid":303111,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T02:10:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170630/s00001/a226dc5fdb40c445c14bda6338be3df4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170630%2Fs00001%2Fa226dc5fdb40c445c14bda6338be3df4.jpg&h=2658717e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170630/s00001/1498785694922\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170630%2Fs00001%2F1498785694922&d=jdE0CXUA4ZDiSTzF1B2RBsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=a873feb1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170630%2Fs00001%2F1498785694922&h=f56f1523\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170630/s00001/1498785694922</a><br />\n<br />\n國家主席習近平訪港第二日，首站將到石崗軍營閱兵。今早5時許，過百名中港及海外記者在灣仔運動場集合，經初步安檢後再乘車到石崗軍營，再進行較仔細的檢查，包括搜身及袋內物品。 <br />\n<br />\n為確保閱兵過程安全，駐軍早前向已報名採訪傳媒發放採訪細節，當中列明數十項物品不得帶進會場，包括筆、水、防曬乳、傘、手機充電器等，但今早有記者被發現有筆或防曬用品仍准帶入。<br />\n<br />\n而經過安檢進到會場後，機構向記者派發日製筆及禮物袋，禮物袋裡有約10項物品，除水、雨傘和毛巾仔等外，亦有國旗、區旗，以及藥油、餅乾等乾糧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170630/s00001/a1d86536d25ac2bf4fd50ba104ce0fcb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170630%2Fs00001%2Fa1d86536d25ac2bf4fd50ba104ce0fcb.jpg&h=29904783&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成個袋最貴可能就係支三菱原子筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90e6cfaff1048cfd77cfde63dabc1e90776707dc","tid":303111,"uid":13663,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T02:11:25.000Z","msg":"人地整唔到原子筆架"},{"pid":"051716b0b599a043da20481d03d7b331c840112e","tid":303111,"uid":1082,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T02:12:11.000Z","msg":"大陸有老番三菱原子筆"},{"pid":"c56c023f5c4ec51b8ddaf9105d0e215c210517af","tid":303111,"uid":33456,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T02:12:14.000Z","msg":"昆仓山水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d28b16c6f965ad2f27c539efd717c781242ed34a","tid":303111,"uid":38523,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T02:12:42.000Z","msg":"笑撚死人支那狗<br />\n冇技術做圓子筆"},{"pid":"c1b6e4f26c2723e69d59baaf83e5f37db5ddbc17","tid":303111,"uid":105498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T02:15:57.000Z","msg":"我都想要呢個套裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39c259f9db20e3d8f970573d1a8bdc797101db6c","tid":303111,"uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T02:17:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71a12f8fdf79cce292c86999b26019a7db81127e","tid":303111,"uid":11001,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T02:21:23.000Z","msg":"航母條arrestor cable咪又係三菱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e276f00b70c6d4fce9d8c4461bd2f059d629c16","tid":303111,"uid":51271,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T02:26:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>航母條arrestor cable咪又係三菱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以原子筆係回佣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a5c4355fdd3a175387fd41a54c69a8abe3ca63","tid":303111,"uid":49392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T02:27:52.000Z","msg":"三菱二戰時整過咩話"