=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n三菱貨車正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25206aa21154d49f536b64b229e914c7aa4c4b9d","tid":303111,"uid":16604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:52:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三菱二戰時整過咩話</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05612a05418b7ca1c700c90e3a513da5ed90dbf7","tid":303111,"uid":115197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:55:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>三菱二戰時整過咩話</blockquote><br />\n戰機？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n文具間三菱同三菱集團冇關係的</blockquote><br />\n有無聽過三菱財閥啊？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nGHQ解散晒所有日本財閥啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n美國人一走又合番埋啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n而家東京咪一樣通地都係住友既物業"},{"pid":"01cdbab54d5c9aed7e2d39453723a9b3472df1cd","tid":303111,"uid":98659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:56:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>三菱二戰時整過咩話</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n在第二次世界大戰期間，三菱在堀越二郎領導之下為日本生產製造武器裝備，其中包括零式戰鬥機、武藏號戰列艦以及各種重型、微型坦克、步兵戰車，軍火產品範圍涵蓋陸海空。共生產各類飛機18000架、坦克裝甲車4650輛。[1]三菱在那段時間裏使用了大量的從日本佔領區擄掠來的苦役勞工[2]。三菱材料公司及舊日本政府在二戰期間強擄3563名中國人到日本9個地方工作，其中704人死亡。2010年8月，部份受害者打算在山東提出索償，三菱總公司已承認指控並願意負責。<br />\n<br />\n三菱係軍國主義集團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5205b8208ac26b25237271b7558be2eaeb659586","tid":303111,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:06:31.000Z","msg":"內戰果時都有班前日軍幫解放軍打仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cbad09acab86d4dae60d267fdf3903e3ad96c2e","tid":303111,"uid":89861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:09:53.000Z","msg":"Made in china"},{"pid":"31c895370296c2558b129dc26ff1b113ec0642a4","tid":303111,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:09:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>三菱二戰時整過咩話</blockquote><br />\n戰機？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n文具間三菱同三菱集團冇關係的</blockquote><br />\n有無聽過三菱財閥啊？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nGHQ解散晒所有日本財閥啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n美國人一走又合番埋啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n而家東京咪一樣通地都係住友既物業</blockquote><br />\n三菱鉛筆同三菱集團都唔係同一個人開，又關ghq差事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a30c0e78b62151fc52b3ab3a7e7b03268ccc239e","tid":303111,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:17:30.000Z","msg":"聽日就會見到好多廢老 拎住呢個 仲有支撚屌旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反清復明啦"},{"pid":"621ff620126812af281a21e7c4f103f5084e8417","tid":303111,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:19:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三菱二戰時整過咩話</blockquote><br />\n依整F35"},{"pid":"cdb8431b4196c4a7da25319ed3acfc1a73f5f31e","tid":303111,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:20:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>三菱二戰時整過咩話</blockquo